OL,5,G1900 Ben Fogle: New Lives in the Wild
OL,6,     FBen journeys into Zambia to live
OL,7,     Fwith a British family who have
OL,8,     Fbuilt a safari lodge on the edge
OL,9,     Fof a national park, overcoming
OL,10,     Ffire, flooding and dangerous
OL,11,     Fwildlife.
OL,12,G2000 Ben Fogle: New Lives in the Wild
OL,13,     FBen travels to the small remote
OL,14,     Fisland of Flores - home to Magnus,
OL,15,     FLucy and one-year-old Frey, who
OL,16,     Flive in an off-grid cottage on a
OL,17,     Fsteep sloped mountain.
